thread.title: Ian Pike

author: Ian Pike
title: Ian Pike
text:
I initially tried to obtain new toner cartridges from my machine supplier. Unfortunately I could not understand that lady who answered the phone.
hen I spoke to Printzone I spoke to a man who clearly understood what I wanted, was himself clear to understand and took my orders which wreduly delivered. The second order was delivered in less that 24 hours.
